                     <interp inst="t18240407-39-person410" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw him running. A gentleman apprehended him, and gave him to me. Way came up and said he was the man.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming up Sun-street, heard an alarm, and pursued a man, a gentleman came up and said I was the man.</p>
